release_note: Share extension no longer presents keyboard.
Added haptic feedback improved localization and a couple more improvements.
Small improvements!
We listened to our users and added lots of features! Easily transcribe in the background to keep using your phone! Listen to your audio file without leaving checkmarks And many more improvements!
We fixed some small errors
Added some more previews to show users how easy it is to transcribe anything in your favourite app.
We have made it easier to leave us a review
Finally supporting Telegram. We know it took us a while.
New screenshots and bug solved while saving messages. Japanese now supported as well
Added support to Portuguese and Italian
Killed a bug. Intentionally.
Solved a bug that hid the transcription.
Improvements here and there
Now it is possible to transcribe the messages in the background and continue using WhatsApp. In other words: we do the dirty work behind the curtains.
Added version info
Improved settings
It is now possible to share the app with friends
Add button to rate app
Better handling of errors
Minor improvements to transcribe long audio messages
We fixed a bug that prevented the app from always transcribing messages of more than one minute. Finally!
Now accessible as share extension!
Fixed localization
